---
title: Chermoula-Yoghurt Chicken with Jewelled Garlic Rice
description: Add a little sparkle to your weeknight dinner with this bright and richly flavoured chicken meal. The “jewels” in the colourful rice are lightly cooked greens, toasted almonds and plump currants, creating an easy and addictive dish that will steal your heart.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/chermoula-yoghurt-chicken-ad08a647.jpg
